Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 011—\NTears sparkling in sunrise{NOTE:涙に映える夕陽}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:44.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H141414&\3c&H141414&\t(0,2000,\1c&H9AFBDC&\3c&H202020&)}Coffee Shop "Alice"{NOTE:喫茶店アリス}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They did come after all.{NOTE:やっぱり来たわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She brought the girls from Toukai's volleyball club.{NOTE:一緒にいたのは東海中学のバレー部よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the former member of\hthe\hHamaki's Big Four want from us?{NOTE:元浜紀中四天王の泉さんはあたしたちに一体何の話があるって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us.{NOTE:早く言って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this "talk important to our club" about?{NOTE:それもあたしたちのバレー部のためになる話Xなんて何なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually…{NOTE:実は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to win the tomorrow's district qualifiers—{NOTE:明日の地区予選の決勝戦ね…是非あんたたちに勝ってもらいたいと思って—}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?{NOTE:本気なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful.{NOTE:酷い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive her.{NOTE:許せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?{NOTE:知ってる?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit the volleyball club.{NOTE:あたしバレー部を辞めたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard about this.{NOTE:それは聞いてたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered why you quit the club myself.{NOTE:どうして辞めたんだろうと思ってたなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't really want to quit.{NOTE:あたしだって辞めたくなかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we merged with Fujimi Academy, their team saw us as a hindrance.{NOTE:でも、富士見学園のバレー部は合併したあたしたちは邪魔だったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They conspired to drive me, a captain, out.{NOTE:それでキャプテンをしていたあたしを追い出そうと企てたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel, don't you think?{NOTE:酷いでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt terrible.{NOTE:それは酷い目に遭ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remembering it is painful.{NOTE:思い出しでも悔しくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up in tears.{NOTE:本当に涙が出るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my sympathy.{NOTE:分かるわ、気持ち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened next?{NOTE:それで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The originators were Ayuhara\hKozue and Hayakawa\hMidori.{NOTE:その張本人は鮎原こずえと早川みどりなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These two want to keep Fujimi\hAcademy's volleyball club to themselves.{NOTE:二人は富士見学園バレー部を自分たちだけのものにしておきたいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thing to say!{NOTE:ま。何てこと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!{NOTE:しい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.{NOTE:静に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If this concerned only me, I'd endure it in peace.{NOTE:あたし一人で我慢て済むことは、そうするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But… but…!{NOTE:でも、でもさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow such people to be elected in the district qualifiers and proceed to the All-Japan Tournament.{NOTE:そう言う人達が地区代表として、全日本の大会に(XXX・必定する)ことはどうしても許せないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.{NOTE:ん。そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to seize the club for oneself is unforgivable.{NOTE:バレーを自分達だけのものにしようなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's…{NOTE:だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'd like you to win the tomorrow's match.{NOTE:あしたの決勝戦を是非あんたたちに勝ってもらいたいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To ensure it…{NOTE:それでね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,…I will tell you the Fujimi's strategy and members' weak points.{NOTE:富士見学園の作戦とメンバーを欠点を教えるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These six are their regulars.{NOTE:この六人はレギュラーメンバーよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means, you need to mark both Ayuhara and Hayakawa.{NOTE:鮎原と早川と二人は決定的にマークすること。いい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Katori's aim is precise.{NOTE:香取は(XX・前方のはうまいけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's weak with side attacks.{NOTE:(XXX・左右)は弱いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her right side is particularly bad.{NOTE:得に左をつけば絶対よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on to Kudou.{NOTE:それから、工藤はね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How low!{NOTE:なんて卑怯な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much she wants to see us fail,\Nbetraying her friends is unthinkable.{NOTE:いくらあたしたちを勝たしたくないから、一緒にやってきたチームメイトまで裏切るなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?{NOTE:どうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we stop them?{NOTE:やる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than taking them on now, we\hshould focus on the tomorrow's match.{NOTE:今彼女取っちめりより、先ず明日の決勝戦に勝つことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.30,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We won't lose.{NOTE:負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fscy90}Toukai district middle school volleyball championship\NCity Gym{NOTE:東海地区中学校バレー選手権大会\\N市立体育館}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how frustrating.{NOTE:あ…苦しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going!{NOTE:いいぞ。XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!{NOTE:頑張れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.31,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,Fujimi ・ Toukai{NOTE:富士見中・東海中}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another captain Ayuhara Kozue's splendid spike hits the court.{NOTE:又も、キャプテン鮎原こずえのスパイクが見事決まりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Having advanced to the All-Japan's final district qualifying match…{NOTE:全日本女子中学バレー部をXXXは予選の決勝に来て、}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,…Fujimi Academy continues to attack fiercely.{NOTE:富士見学園の猛攻が爆発XXX漢字で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!{NOTE:いいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Fujimi's performance cannot be compared to yesterday's match with Sone.{NOTE:昨日の曽根中学との大戦で、あれほどXXX富士見学園とは思うありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?{NOTE:ほらほら、何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!{NOTE:ワアアイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.51,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,Fujimi ・ Toukai{NOTE:富士見中・東海中}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.{NOTE:頑張って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Ayuhara-kun!{NOTE:いいぞ、鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!{NOTE:その調子だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!{NOTE:頑張れぇぇえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.48,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{NOTE:どうしたXか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.65,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The strategy was changed.{NOTE:作戦を変えた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.44,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if they figured out my plan.{NOTE:丸でこっちの計画をXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.91,Alternative,,0,0,0,,At any rate, Ayuhara Kozue sure is strong.{NOTE:それにしても、鮎原こずえは強いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate you so much.{NOTE:だからあたしはあんたを憎いんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like shuffling the squad has paid off.{NOTE:(XXX・なのついたではね)裏をかかれてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate we've already won.{NOTE:このままでいただきね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent has trained for All-Japan games too.{NOTE:開いても全日本の大会出るために必死よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.{NOTE:XXXけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?{NOTE:ね、一体どうなっただろう?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what she promised to us.{NOTE:話とでは全然違うじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They went with different players. The strategy's wrong too.{NOTE:メンバーも変わってるし、作戦は全然治が上。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been tricked.{NOTE:あたしたちは騙されたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange.{NOTE:可笑しいと思ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would betray their school.{NOTE:自分の学校を裏切る人なんかいないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's painful, but we're fools for having believed her.{NOTE:悔しいけど真に受けたあたしたちは馬鹿だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.{NOTE:もう遅いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one point left.{NOTE:後ワンポイントでお終いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try until end.{NOTE:最後まで頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do much else.{NOTE:もうそれしかないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:さ、行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's do this!\N– Good luck!{NOTE:—行きましょう。\\N—頑張ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!{NOTE:ちょっと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!{NOTE:Xよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.89,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,Fujimi ・ Toukai{NOTE:富士見中・東海中}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!{NOTE:ワアアイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!{NOTE:ヤホオ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We won, we won!{NOTE:勝ったわ、勝ったわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.{NOTE:よかった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,– Professor!\N– Professor!{NOTE:—先生！\\N—先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you! You did well.{NOTE:皆！よく頑張った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With today's victory, we became our district's representatives.{NOTE:しかし、いいか。今日勝ったといっても、地区予選の代表に成ったXだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't mean you can take it easy now.{NOTE:お前たち。地区代表ぐらいXXないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One week until the All-Japan Tournament.{NOTE:全国大会まで後一週間。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The participants will be the best schools in the whole country.{NOTE:その時には、全国からXXの代表が集まる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The truly difficult games are yet ahead.{NOTE:本当に苦しい試合がこれからX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.{NOTE:それを忘れない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,– Got it?\N– Yes.{NOTE:—分かったな？\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yeah.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,– Congratulations!\N– Congratulations!{NOTE:—おめでとう！\\N—おめでとう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.{NOTE:よかったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!{NOTE:よかった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats!{NOTE:おめでとう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it to the All-Japan Tournament.{NOTE:これで全国大会必定だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you together with Izumi-san?{NOTE:泉さんは一緒じゃなかったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Err…{NOTE:え？お…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she went to.{NOTE:どこへ行ったかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I saw her come here.{NOTE:確かに、来ただようだったけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd come, no?{NOTE:来られるわけがないでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean?{NOTE:え？どう言う意味だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Izumi-san thinks we should lose.{NOTE:だって、泉さんはあたしたちが負ければいいと思ってるんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be. Izumi-kun is not like that.{NOTE:そんなことはないさ。泉くんは人じゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun is—{NOTE:泉くんは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.{NOTE:いいのよ、もう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-san, I don't want to listen to it.{NOTE:努さん、聞きたくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a chance to see her true colors yesterday.{NOTE:あの人はね、どんな人か、はっきり分かったんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kozue-san?{NOTE:ね、こずえさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls…{NOTE:君達…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are we doing here?{NOTE:一体何のようがあるだ、こんな所で?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be patient.{NOTE:もう少し待ってて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to show you something, Tsutomu-san.{NOTE:努さんに見せたいものがあるだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!{NOTE:来た！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here.{NOTE:来たわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:ほ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun!{NOTE:泉くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show you what kind of\hperson Izumi-san is really like.{NOTE:泉さんは一体どんな人か、見せてあげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san.{NOTE:泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san. Did you see our match today?{NOTE:泉さん。今日の試合見てくれた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted us to lose and here we are, having won by a landslide. Disappointed, hm?{NOTE:負ければいいと思って、あたしたちが軽く勝ったので、あなたがっかりしてるんでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.{NOTE:笑えせないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to boast to me this badly?{NOTE:今日勝ったことそんなにあたしに自慢したいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You even came to ambush me in such a place.{NOTE:それでこんな所であたしを待ち伏せていたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it.{NOTE:そうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway…{NOTE:それにさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you won, what of it?{NOTE:勝ったと言っても、XXXじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think the tournament will be as\heasy as today, you're terribly mistaken.{NOTE:全国大会でまた今日のようにうまく行くと思ったら、とんでもない間違いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?{NOTE:そう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see us lose so much?{NOTE:そんなにあたしたちを負けたXいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you win or lose doesn't concern me.{NOTE:あんたたちの勝とうや負けようか、あたしには全然関係のないことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in your club anymore. Remember?{NOTE:あたしはもうバレー部員じゃないんですから。そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!{NOTE:惚けないでよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what do you mean?{NOTE:あら、何のこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you drag this farce?{NOTE:どこまで惚けるつもりなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is absurd.{NOTE:涼しいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you spy for and for how long?{NOTE:スパイのまでなんかしたのは一体どこのだれなの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Spy?{NOTE:スパイ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make weird accusations.{NOTE:変な言い掛かりよしてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san. We went to the same coffee shop yesterday as you.{NOTE:泉さん、昨日あたしたちはあなたと同じ喫茶店にいたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw you meet girls from the Toukai's volleyball club.{NOTE:あなたが東海中学のバレー部の人達と話してる時に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You told them the Fujimi Academy team's strategy and the members' weaknesses.{NOTE:バレー部員だったあなたが富士見学園チームの作戦や決定を試合の相手に知らせるなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?{NOTE:これは一体どう言うことなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun!{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What they just said is true?!{NOTE:きみ、今の話は本当なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you say something?{NOTE:何とか言ったらどうなのよ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san, did you forget our time together in the volleyball club?{NOTE:泉さん、あたしたちXXXバレー部から追い出したりしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not just about us.{NOTE:それに、あたしたちのことばかりじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What if your friends, what if Kudou-san, Katori-san heard us now?{NOTE:同じ仲間だった、工藤さんや香取さんが、このこと聞いたら、何と思うかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How much effort did every one of us put into that club?{NOTE:皆XXXバレーボールがXXX優勝するためにどれだけ一所懸命努力してるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it very well.{NOTE:あなたはよく知ってるじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of your actions?{NOTE:あんな卑怯なこと…恥ずかしくないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did losing to us hurt you so much?{NOTE:あたしたちに負けたことはそんなに悔しいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why… why don't we settle it through volleyball?{NOTE:だったら…だったらバレーでもつかってくればいいじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we work together? Why don't we play volleyball together and form a strong team?{NOTE:あたしたちと一緒に…あたしたちと一緒にバレーをやってあたしたちを任すぐらい強く成ればいいじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do such thing?{NOTE:どうしてそんなことをしたんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.{NOTE:放っといてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I quit, I didn't want to!{NOTE:あたしだって辞めたって、辞めたいじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I went through it anyway.{NOTE:それほど続けたかったか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-san, you know it the best.{NOTE:努さん、よく知ってるじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that part.{NOTE:それは分かっているさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But this doesn't mean it justifies what you did.{NOTE:でも、だからと言って、そんなことをしてもいいと言うことには…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand me.{NOTE:分かってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun!{NOTE:泉くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one understands me.{NOTE:だれにもあたしのことなんか分からないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun!{NOTE:泉くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-san.{NOTE:努さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean?{NOTE:一体どうしたて言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to Izumi-san?{NOTE:泉さんに何があったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun didn't quit because she has lost to you.{NOTE:泉くんはバレー部を辞めたらは君達に負けた所為じゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the shock from it surely played some part.{NOTE:いや、もちろん…そのショックも少しXったけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But the main reason is that she couldn't bend her wrist.{NOTE:実は、手首の具合が悪くて自分の思うように重くなかったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The wrist?{NOTE:手首？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand.{NOTE:手が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts…!{NOTE:痛い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So she must've hurt it around that time when she hit the ball.{NOTE:じゃ、あの時ボールが手首に当たったのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it was aching from time to time even before that.{NOTE:や、前から時々具合が悪かったんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said she put too\hmuch stress on her wrist.{NOTE:医者は言うにはなんでも見に手首をXX使いすぎだXXってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. That's how it was.{NOTE:あ。そうだったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the doctor ordered her to\htake a break from volleyball.{NOTE:医者にバレーボールは絶対に休むようにって言われたんでそうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, Izumi-kun…{NOTE:だけど、泉くんはね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… it hurts.{NOTE:あ。痛い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you playing again?{NOTE:又やってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do this.{NOTE:止めなさいX分からないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor has said it too.{NOTE:お医者さんにXでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He ordered you to take a break from volleyball for half a year.{NOTE:半年ぐらいは絶対にバレーをやってらいけませんって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.{NOTE:止めなさい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am returning to the club as their captain.{NOTE:あたしは又キャプテンとしてバレー部に戻るんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This means I must get stronger than anyone else.{NOTE:そのためには誰よりも誰よりも強くなくちゃいけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A break is the least what I need now.{NOTE:そんなにXX休んでなんか要られないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you endure it for half a year?{NOTE:半年ぐらい我慢できないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,– Stop it!\N– Oh!{NOTE:—止めなさい！\\N—お！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the ball back!{NOTE:ボール返してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!{NOTE:あ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.{NOTE:放っといてよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand nothing about volleyball.{NOTE:あんたなんかにバレーのこと分かるもんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we're constructing a dam.{NOTE:今度はダムの建設だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's near the mountains so\NI won't be home for a while.{NOTE:山の中だから、今までよりXX帰XXだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make your mom worry too much when I'm out.{NOTE:お父さんがいない間、お母さんにあんまり心配をかけないよにな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll give up that volleyball thing, no?{NOTE:バレーの練習なんかやめるんだぞ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.{NOTE:いやよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It healed already. See?{NOTE:もう大丈夫よ。ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not get it?{NOTE:未だ分からんのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor told you to stop, no?{NOTE:医者はバレーをやっちゃいけないと言っただろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?{NOTE:いいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:分かったな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized who has asked the\hdoctor for such a diagnosis.{NOTE:だれががお医者さんXXに言うように頼んだのを知ってるは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a certain someone who hates me.{NOTE:あたしを憎んでるだれがさんが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{NOTE:何てことを言うんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman hates me.{NOTE:この人はあたしを憎いのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she tries to make me part with volleyball.{NOTE:だから、あたしからこの人はバレーを取り上げ落としてるんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you speak like that to your mom?{NOTE:お母さんに向かってお前は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman isn't my mom!{NOTE:こんな人はあたしのお母さんじゃないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom…{NOTE:あたしのお母さんはね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,…was nicer and had a gentle heart!{NOTE:もっとやさしく、心の美しい人だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{NOTE:お待ちなさい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right hand's…{NOTE:お前の右手は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!{NOTE:あなた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She fights with her current mom so much.{NOTE:今の母さんにくられて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She sees her to be inferior to the biological mother, who has passed away.{NOTE:そんなXXになんてなくなったお母さんはことが尚更いい人を思えるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't settle for taking a six months long break.{NOTE:バレーは半年も休まなければいけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus she fights with her mom.{NOTE:その上お母さんとうまくいかない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I talked with her…{NOTE:泉くんに話を聞いたとき…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really know what to tell her.{NOTE:僕はどう答えていた分からなくてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop crying.{NOTE:さ、もう泣くの止せよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If people saw us, they'd jump to conclusions.{NOTE:人に見られたら、変に思われずね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.{NOTE:いいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't take it any more.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel down.{NOTE:そんなやけをお越し駄目だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, okay, Izumi-kun?{NOTE:冷静に成るんだ。ね、泉くん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Izumi-kun.{NOTE:ね、泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you back then.{NOTE:(XXX・かれし)じなかったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's talk to her again.{NOTE:ね、もう一度泉さんと話してましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.{NOTE:あなたは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do you want?{NOTE:なによ？何だって言うのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like going to school.{NOTE:学校行くのは嫌なったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Leave me be.{NOTE:それだけよ。放っといてよ、ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you quit the school and go to Tokyo.{NOTE:学校止めて、東京へ行くなんて、そんなことは絶対にいけません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive it.{NOTE:許しませんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri.{NOTE:ね、ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, listen to what I'm saying.{NOTE:お願いだから、あたしの言うことを聞いて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!{NOTE:いやよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't listen to you.{NOTE:あんたの言うことなんか聞きたくないんだったら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be better off if I wasn't here, wouldn't you?{NOTE:あたしなんかいなくなった方があんたもいいんでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,– I know that—\N– Yuri!{NOTE:—分かってるわよ。\\N—ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care what happens to me after all.{NOTE:どうせあたしなんか…どうなったて構わないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was jealous of you, who could play volleyball.{NOTE:バレーのできる君達は嫉ましかったんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she did it all and betrayed you\h– she wanted you to feel the pain too.{NOTE:それであんなことまでして、皆を裏切って、今泉くんはどれほど辛いおもいをしてるか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:39.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,Izumi family{NOTE:泉}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!{NOTE:小母さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.{NOTE:小母さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ichinose-san.{NOTE:あ、一ノ瀬さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?{NOTE:何か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I…{NOTE:私…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…argued with Yuri…{NOTE:ゆりと嫌になって、つい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…and all of the sudden, she fled home.{NOTE:そうしたら、いきなり家から飛び出して…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look for her.{NOTE:あたしたちは探していきます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.{NOTE:頼むよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.{NOTE:小母さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told her clearly.{NOTE:あたしははっきり言えばよかったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't.{NOTE:でも、どうしても言えなくて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, ma'am?{NOTE:小母さん、何をですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san.{NOTE:泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard it from Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努さんから聞いた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no idea about your wrist condition.{NOTE:手首の具合は悪いなんて…知らなかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us?{NOTE:どうして話してくれなかったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point?{NOTE:話して何、何の?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want your sympathy.{NOTE:同情何かしてほしくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't intend to be sympathetic.{NOTE:別に同情なんかしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wrist is no good. You quit the volleyball club and it can't be helped. Am I right?{NOTE:手首が悪いじゃ、バレーを止めれX仕方ないじゃないの。そうじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you entered the track and field club.{NOTE:だからあなた陸上部で入ったんでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you try your earnest in your new club?{NOTE:だったら、陸上部で一所懸命にやればいいじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you do that?{NOTE:それがどうしてできないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.{NOTE:あ、そうっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the volleyball club, you had your Big Four fame.{NOTE:バレーでは四天王と言われてほど有名だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the new club you'd start from scratch.{NOTE:それが陸上部に入れば、一からやり直し。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You were anxious whether you could repeat this success.{NOTE:バレー部の時のように有名に成るかどうか、不安なんでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why you had no motivation.{NOTE:だからやる気がないのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!{NOTE:違うわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found out I couldn't play volleyball, I\hwanted to give the track and field club my all.{NOTE:バレーをできない間…せめて陸上部に入った一所懸命やろうとしたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't forget about volleyball.{NOTE:でも、どうしてもバレーのことも忘れられなくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you chose the track and field club.{NOTE:でも、あなたは陸上部選んだのは—}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were confident you could run well, no?{NOTE:走り自身があったからでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when you joined, it turned out to be more demanding than you thought.{NOTE:(所が)陸上部に入ってやってみると思ったより苦しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So your motivation dropped.{NOTE:それを自身無くした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bummer.{NOTE:だらしが無いのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?{NOTE:あら、どうかしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty rude!{NOTE:酷い言い方するのね、あなたって—}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm right, am I not?{NOTE:だってその通りでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your way of thinking is naive.{NOTE:天井のよ。あなたの考え方は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go further, I won't keep silent.{NOTE:そこまで言われて、黙っていられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?{NOTE:どうするって言うの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we compete right now?{NOTE:あたしと競争でもしてみる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can win, though.{NOTE:でも、あなたに勝てるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My time for 100 meters is 13 seconds.{NOTE:あたしは百メートル十三秒よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?{NOTE:ちょっとむりじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.{NOTE:負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to the likes of you.{NOTE:あんたなんかに負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.{NOTE:やりましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then…{NOTE:じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to circle that tree and returns, wins.{NOTE:一番のこの松の木前でしましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right about 100 meters.{NOTE:ちょうど百メートルぐらいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san, please give us a signal.{NOTE:みどりさん、スターとお願い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On your marks.{NOTE:位置について。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:19.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ayuhara-san plans to lose on purpose to help Izumi-san regain her confidence?{NOTE:泉さんに自身をつけさせるため、鮎原さんは負けるつもりなのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.38,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.{NOTE:負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.25,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I will surely win.{NOTE:絶対勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get set!{NOTE:よい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.{NOTE:負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.31,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.{NOTE:負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.52,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!{NOTE:負けるもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.74,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!{NOTE:負けられないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.20,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!{NOTE:負けるもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.24,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose…!{NOTE:負けるもんか…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:08.79,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose…{NOTE:負けるもんかぁ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner is Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さんの勝ちだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known losing on\hpurpose isn't Ayuhara-san's style.{NOTE:わざと負けるなんて…やっぱり鮎原さんのらしくないもんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I won.{NOTE:あたしの勝ちね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard…{NOTE:どんなに苦しくても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how harsh…{NOTE:どんなに辛くても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing something with all your might feels great.{NOTE:自分の全力を(XXX・出すXXX素敵)ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sensation of sportsmanship.{NOTE:それはスポーツをする人の気持ちなのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People using traps aren't entitled to it.{NOTE:それはXXXスポーツをする資格はないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though your mom cares about you, you\hdon't understand her feelings and fight her.{NOTE:お母さんのことにしても、あなたはお母さんのやさしい気持ちを分かると努力しないじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight with your mom.{NOTE:お母さんの気持ちも分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get sportsmanship.{NOTE:スポーツをする心も分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A person like you has no business with either volleyball or track and field club.{NOTE:そんな人は…バレーだって、陸上だって…皆やめてしまいはいいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:さ。行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I…{NOTE:あたし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,…will keep running.{NOTE:走るわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't quit!{NOTE:止めないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about your wrist.{NOTE:君のこの手首はね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffer from arterial occlusion.{NOTE:動脈閉塞症で、}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue volleyball,\Nyour wrist will give out completely.{NOTE:これ以上バレーを続けると、君の手首は…まったく駄目に成っちゃうんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{NOTE:どう言うことなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do volleyball ever again.{NOTE:もう二度とバレーはできないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor has made himself clear.{NOTE:医者ははっきりそう言ったんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mom couldn't tell it to you.{NOTE:お母さんは君にそこまでは言えなかったんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, she softened it and told you to stop for half a year.{NOTE:だから、半年ぐらい休めばと言うことにして、}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She planned to talk you out of it\Nsomehow during that period.{NOTE:君にバレーを何とかして諦めさせをおとしなんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun.{NOTE:泉くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.{NOTE:お母さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!{NOTE:お母さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hit the ball hard, it's okay.{NOTE:ボールを強く打ったりしなければ大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told you the truth from the start.{NOTE:最初からはっきり言えばよかったんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was unable to tell you to give up volleyball forever.{NOTE:もう二度とバレーはできないだなんて…どうしても言えなかったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!{NOTE:お母さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I…{NOTE:あたし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…will try.{NOTE:やってみる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best in the track and field club.{NOTE:陸上部でやってみるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put in the same strength I put into volleyball.{NOTE:バレーに全力でぶつかったと同じよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:55.75,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The first match in All-Japan Tournament draws near.{NOTE:念願の全国大会初出場は成った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:57.87,Alternative,,0,0,0,,"You have what it takes to win."{NOTE:「君達には優勝する実力がある。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.96,Alternative,,0,0,0,,— professor Hongou encourages the girls.{NOTE:…と本郷コーチは保証する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:03.42,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The Fujimi Academy team goes to Tokyo.{NOTE:富士見学園チームはXXなって、東京に向かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:04.88,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The nostalgic Tokyo.{NOTE:懐かしい東京。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:07.63,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kozue visits the Meihou Academy.{NOTE:こずえはXX明法学園を訪れた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:12.97,Alternative,,0,0,0,,In the Meihou's gym, she meets powerful peers from Fukuoka Middle School in the middle of practice.{NOTE:だが、明法の体育館で練習中の福岡中学を見て、XX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:16.31,Alternative,,0,0,0,,One of them knows a receive technique way above middle schoolers level.{NOTE:中学生には及びもつかないレシーブを知っている戦士がいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:19.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kozue's confidence quickly collapses.{NOTE:こずえの自身は俄に崩れかかる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:22.82,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
